">Leah</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Leo\" title=\"Leo\"><img alt=\"Leo Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/3/3d/Leo_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Leo\" title=\"Leo\">Leo</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Lewis\" title=\"Lewis\"><img alt=\"Lewis Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b6/Lewis_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Lewis\" title=\"Lewis\">Lewis</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Linus\" title=\"Linus\"><img alt=\"Linus Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/db/Linus_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Linus\" title=\"Linus\">Linus</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Marnie\" title=\"Marnie\"><img alt=\"Marnie Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d4/Marnie_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Marnie\" title=\"Marnie\">Marnie</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Maru\" title=\"Maru\"><img alt=\"Maru Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/2/23/Maru_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Maru\" title=\"Maru\">Maru</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Pam\" title=\"Pam\"><img alt=\"Pam Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b6/Pam_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Pam\" title=\"Pam\">Pam</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Penny\" title=\"Penny\"><img alt=\"Penny Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/bc/Penny_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Pierre\" title=\"Pierre\"><img alt=\"Pierre Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/cf/Pierre_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Pierre\" title=\"Pierre\">Pierre</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Robin\" title=\"Robin\"><img alt=\"Robin Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d1/Robin_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Robin\" title=\"Robin\">Robin</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\"><img alt=\"Sam Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/5/52/Sam_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\">Sam</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\"><img alt=\"Sandy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7d/Sandy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\">Sandy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\"><img alt=\"Sebastian Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6a/Sebastian_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\">Sebastian</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\"><img alt=\"Shane Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b4/Shane_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\">Shane</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\"><img alt=\"Vincent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0b/Vincent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\">Vincent</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\"><img alt=\"Willy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/73/Willy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\">Willy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\"><img alt=\"Wizard Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e9/Wizard_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\">Wizard</a></span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bundles\">Bundles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Rain_Totem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Bundles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Rain Totem is not used in any <a href=\"/Bundles\" title=\"Bundles\">bundles</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Rain_Totem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Tailoring\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>A Rain Totem can be used in the spool of the <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">Sewing Machine</a> to create the <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Totem Mask.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/cc/Totem_Mask.png/24px-Totem_Mask.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/cc/Totem_Mask.png/36px-Totem_Mask.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/c/cc/Totem_Mask.png/48px-Totem_Mask.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Totem_Mask\" title=\"Totem Mask\">Totem Mask</a></span>. It can be used in <a href=\"/Dyeing\" title=\"Dyeing\">dyeing</a>, serving as an orange dye at the dye pots, located in <a href=\"/Emily\" title=\"Emily\">Emily</a>'s and <a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\">Haley</a>'s house, <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">2 Willow Lane</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quests\">Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Rain_Totem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Quests\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Rain Totem is not used in any <a href=\"/Quests\" title=\"Quests\">quests</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bugs\">Bugs</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Rain_Totem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Bugs\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>If a Rain Totem is used during <a href=\"/Winter\" title=\"Winter\">Winter</a> on the day before a snowy day, it will cause it to rain and snow simultaneously the following day.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Rain_Totem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Can now be used in <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: Fixed a bug where using a Rain Totem on a stormy day would turn the next day's <a href=\"/Weather\" title=\"Weather\">weather</a> to stormy instead of rainy; storms could be chained in this way to obtain large numbers of <a href=\"/Battery_Pack\" title=\"Battery Pack\">Battery Packs</a>.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Totems\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Warp_Totem\" title=\"Warp Totem\">Warp Totems</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Beach\" title=\"Warp Totem: Beach\">Warp Totem: Beach</a> • <a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Desert\" title=\"Warp Totem: Desert\">Warp Totem: Desert</a> • <a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Farm\" title=\"Warp Totem: Farm\">Warp Totem: Farm</a> • <a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Island\" title=\"Warp Totem: Island\">Warp Totem: Island</a> • <a href=\"/Warp_Totem:_Mountains\" title=\"Warp Totem: Mountains\">Warp Totem: Mountains</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Warp_Totem\" title=\"Warp Totem\">Permanent Teleporters</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Desert_Obelisk\" title=\"Desert Obelisk\">Desert Obelisk</a> • <a href=\"/Earth_Obelisk\" title=\"Earth Obelisk\">Earth Obelisk</a> • <a href=\"/Farm_Obelisk\" title=\"Farm Obelisk\">Farm Obelisk</a> • <a href=\"/Island_Obelisk\" title=\"Island Obelisk\">Island Obelisk</a> • <a href=\"/Return_Scepter\" title=\"Return Scepter\">Return Scepter</a> • <a href=\"/Water_Obelisk\" title=\"Water Obelisk\">Water Obelisk</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Other Totems\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Mini-Obelisk\" title=\"Mini-Obelisk\">Mini-Obelisk</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rain Totem</a> • <a href=\"/Treasure_Totem\" title=\"Treasure Totem\">Treasure Totem</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413232914\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.102 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.119 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1868/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 13051/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1559/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1504/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.003/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 519 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   48.750      1 -total\n 61.54%   30.000      1 Template:Infobox_cooking\n 26.57%   12.951      1 Template:Description\n 26.31%   12.828      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n 24.11%   11.755      4 Template:Name\n  6.39%    3.113      2 Template:History\n  4.55%    2.218      1 Template:Price\n  3.20%    1.559      2 Template:Version\n  3.17%    1.544      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n  3.15%    1.537      1 Template:NavboxWarpTotems\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:3000-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413232914 and revision id 190532\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "<onlyinclude>{{{{{1|Infobox cooking}}}\n|name        = Rain Totem\n|image       = Rain Totem.png\n|description = {{Description|Rain Totem}}\n|source      = [[Crafting]]\n|ingredients = {{Name|Hardwood|1}}{{Name|Truffle Oil|1}}{{Name|Pine Tar|5}}\n|recipe      = <div class=\"no-wrap\">[[File:Foraging Skill Icon.png|24px|link=]] [[Foraging#Foraging Skill|Foraging]] Level 9</div>\n|sellprice   = 20\n|qiseasoning = false\n}}</onlyinclude>\nThe '''Rain Totem''' is a [[Crafting#Consumables|crafted item]] that sets the [[weather]] for the next day to rainy. A Rain Totem can be activated by selecting it in inventory and pressing the [[Controls|''Check'' button]] ([[File:Right-Click.png|24px]] on PC, '''Y''' on Nintendo Switch, '''A''' on Xbox, '''X''' on PlayStation). \n\nThe crafting recipe becomes available at [[Foraging]] Level 9. One to three Rain Totems may also occasionally be found in [[Skull Cavern#Treasure Rooms|treasure rooms]] in the Skull Cavern.\n\n==Caveats==\n*The weather in [[Pelican Town]] and [[Ginger Island]] can be different, and the weather will only be changed in the region where the Rain Totem is activated.\n*A Rain Totem will not force the weather in Pelican Town to be rainy on [[Festivals|festival]] days or on the 1st day of a season.\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|hate=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Sebastian,Linus,Leo,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jas,Vincent,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Krobus\n}}\n\n==Bundles==\nRain Totem is not used in any [[bundles]].\n\n==Tailoring==\nA Rain Totem can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the {{Name|Totem Mask|class=inline}}. It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as an orange dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].\n\n==Quests==\nThe Rain Totem is not used in any [[quests]].\n\n==Bugs==\n*If a Rain Totem is used during [[Winter]] on the day before a snowy day, it will cause it to rain and snow simultaneously the following day.\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}\n{{History|1.6|Fixed a bug where using a Rain Totem on a stormy day would turn the next day's [[weather]] to stormy instead of rainy; storms could be chained in this way to obtain large numbers of [[Battery Pack]]s.}}\n\n{{NavboxWarpTotems}}\n\n[[Category:Craftable items]]\n[[Category:Bugs tested in 1.5]]\n\n[[de:Regentotem]]\n[[es:Tótem de lluvia]]\n[[fr:Totem de pluie]]\n[[it:Totem della pioggia]]\n[[ja:レイントーテム]]\n[[ko:비의 토템]]\n[[hu:Eső totem]]\n[[pt:Totem de chuva]]\n[[ru:Тотем дождя]]\n[[tr:Yağmur Totemi]]\n[[zh:雨水图腾]]"
